Thanks for your feedback. We’ve listened and made improvements to the WU app.

Now you can use the WU® app to send money with our pay cash in-store feature
- Lock the FX and fee for most of the receiver countries 1
- Save all your information for future transfers by completing your transfer as a registered user
- Discover participating agent locations to pay cash in-store for the transfer you initiate on the WU app
_______________________________________________________________
[1] The exchange rate is only advisory and the actual exchange rate will be determined at the time of payout.
